text: With the frills, lace, and sweet pink...

I was a bit worried
if I could pull off this kind of style...

You look fantastic in it.
How about incorporating it into your everyday outings?

But diving straight into it,
might require a bit of courage...
Maybe starting with accessories would be better?

Hehe, Chiyuki's handmade items.
Amana and Tenka would probably want one too.

Hehe, I'd be happy if that's the case.
Matching subtly sounds lovely...
